WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.189
Hey, good morning, family. I'm excited to

00:00:03.199 --> 00:00:05.950
be with you all again today. I'm thinking

00:00:05.950 --> 00:00:05.960
of bringing

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:08.030
on a

00:00:08.030 --> 00:00:08.040
challenge—let's

00:00:08.040 --> 00:00:09.509
do

00:00:09.519 --> 00:00:12.749
something fun together. It

00:00:12.759 --> 00:00:14.430
doesn't always have to be serious when I

00:00:14.440 --> 00:00:16.510
come on here preaching;

00:00:16.520 --> 00:00:18.109
this is just something that is on my

00:00:18.119 --> 00:00:20.550
heart. I feel like it's

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:23.390
easier when we're a team with a

00:00:23.390 --> 00:00:23.400
sense of

00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:26.470
camaraderie. The

00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:28.589
Lord really put it on my heart one day while I

00:00:28.599 --> 00:00:29.950
was praying, and He said to me,

00:00:29.950 --> 00:00:29.960
'Brandon,

00:00:29.960 --> 00:00:32.910
I really want you to take care of

00:00:32.920 --> 00:00:35.030
yourself and get rid of some

00:00:35.030 --> 00:00:35.040
weight.'I

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:36.510
want to get rid of it; I

00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:37.869
don't say 'lose'it because I don't want to find

00:00:37.879 --> 00:00:40.670
it again. I want to

00:00:40.680 --> 00:00:42.750
get rid of it and not go

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:45.750
back into this bad cycle of eating poorly

00:00:45.750 --> 00:00:45.760
and not

00:00:45.760 --> 00:00:48.229
taking care of my body this

00:00:48.239 --> 00:00:50.310
way. It's something that I have struggled

00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:53.950
with my whole life:

00:00:53.960 --> 00:00:56.709
stress eating

00:00:56.719 --> 00:00:59.310
and

00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:01.389
always nibbling on chocolate,

00:01:01.399 --> 00:01:05.509
chips, or

00:01:05.509 --> 00:01:05.519
candy.

00:01:05.519 --> 00:01:08.109
I asked the Lord, 'I have an

00:01:08.119 --> 00:01:10.590
addiction, Lord,

00:01:10.590 --> 00:01:10.600
toward

00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:13.429
bad food,'and it's been a

00:01:13.439 --> 00:01:15.710
stronghold. To be real with y'all,

00:01:15.720 --> 00:01:17.230
we all have stuff we're going

00:01:17.240 --> 00:01:19.070
through, but this is something that I

00:01:19.080 --> 00:01:21.590
deal with and it's been

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:24.429
a real

00:01:24.439 --> 00:01:26.350
issue with me. To be real

00:01:26.360 --> 00:01:27.910
with you, I'm

00:01:28.840 --> 00:01:32.670
304 pounds right now. I'm 5'11"and 304

00:01:32.670 --> 00:01:32.680
pounds,

00:01:32.680 --> 00:01:35.950
and

00:01:35.960 --> 00:01:38.910
that's too big. The Lord said,

00:01:38.920 --> 00:01:41.710
'Brandon, I need you to lose 100

00:01:41.720 --> 00:01:43.910
pounds.'When

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:47.389
I get down to 204

00:01:47.389 --> 00:01:47.399
pounds,

00:01:47.399 --> 00:01:49.749
we'll see where we are then, but

00:01:49.759 --> 00:01:52.429
I'm believing God that in

00:01:52.439 --> 00:01:55.230
2024 I'm going to do the things

00:01:55.240 --> 00:01:58.270
I need to do to achieve

00:01:58.280 --> 00:02:00.749
that goal. I know that it's not going

00:02:00.759 --> 00:02:03.749
to just fall off of me by eating the way

00:02:03.759 --> 00:02:07.109
I still did, so I'm going to change it

00:02:07.119 --> 00:02:10.869
up. People have

00:02:10.879 --> 00:02:13.550
given me emails about keto and

00:02:13.550 --> 00:02:13.560
the

00:02:13.560 --> 00:02:16.390
carnivore diet, so there

00:02:16.390 --> 00:02:16.400
are

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:18.110
a lot of people that feel like I

00:02:18.120 --> 00:02:20.630
need to lose weight;

00:02:20.640 --> 00:02:22.190
it's not just the Lord. I'm going to

00:02:22.200 --> 00:02:25.470
start off doing ketogenic and I

00:02:25.480 --> 00:02:28.110
believe I can do this doing keto and

00:02:28.120 --> 00:02:31.430
more carnivore—not doing strictly keto,

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:34.190
but eating the meats and

00:02:34.200 --> 00:02:36.110
cutting sweets out completely. I'm not

00:02:36.120 --> 00:02:37.710
going to do sweets,

00:02:37.720 --> 00:02:40.309
breads, pastas, or things like

00:02:40.309 --> 00:02:40.319
that—no

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:42.430
cookies, I'm cutting it all

00:02:42.440 --> 00:02:45.229
out. I'm cutting out the treats and

00:02:45.239 --> 00:02:48.390
no sugary sodas. I'm

00:02:48.390 --> 00:02:48.400
going to

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:50.790
really

00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:54.589
fine-tune this thing: exercise, take

00:02:54.599 --> 00:02:57.309
care of my heart, take care of my body,

00:02:57.319 --> 00:03:01.830
and focus on being a healthier me in

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:05.070
2024.

00:03:05.080 --> 00:03:06.789
Every week, I'll come on here

00:03:06.799 --> 00:03:08.750
and tell you how much I've lost or even

00:03:08.760 --> 00:03:10.910
if I've gained something, but

00:03:10.920 --> 00:03:12.750
I'm believing God that the scale is

00:03:12.760 --> 00:03:14.509
going the other way. My wife said,

00:03:14.519 --> 00:03:16.750
'Brandon, you're handsome regardless of

00:03:16.760 --> 00:03:18.430
how you look,

00:03:18.440 --> 00:03:20.910
but it would be good

00:03:20.920 --> 00:03:22.830
if you lost 100 pounds just for your

00:03:22.840 --> 00:03:26.350
health.'So,

00:03:26.360 --> 00:03:29.190
I'm going to do this, but not only lose

00:03:29.200 --> 00:03:30.750
it, I'm going to keep it off so I don't

00:03:30.760 --> 00:03:32.750
want to find it ever again. I don't want

00:03:32.760 --> 00:03:35.190
to be on the roller coaster diet.

00:03:35.190 --> 00:03:35.200
You

00:03:35.200 --> 00:03:37.470
all saw me in that one

00:03:37.480 --> 00:03:39.949
video, my tribulation video, when I

00:03:39.959 --> 00:03:41.589
went to the throne room of the Lord. I

00:03:41.599 --> 00:03:44.869
was doing packet foods called Sanford

00:03:44.869 --> 00:03:44.879
by

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:48.309
Profile.

00:03:48.319 --> 00:03:50.429
I was eating five times

00:03:50.439 --> 00:03:53.110
a day—1,000 calories a day plus a

00:03:53.120 --> 00:03:55.710
lean and

00:03:55.710 --> 00:03:55.720
green—and

00:03:55.720 --> 00:04:00.030
I lost 80 pounds over that year because

00:04:00.040 --> 00:04:01.710
it was just on my heart. I was heavy

00:04:01.720 --> 00:04:03.589
and I needed to do it.

00:04:03.599 --> 00:04:05.390
I got a

00:04:05.400 --> 00:04:07.309
weight loss coach and he was really good,

00:04:07.319 --> 00:04:09.589
a nice guy, and

00:04:09.599 --> 00:04:11.429
every

00:04:11.439 --> 00:04:13.910
single week I weighed in and

00:04:13.920 --> 00:04:16.030
they kept on me. Well, I didn't want to

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:18.629
pay the $1,500 again to do the

00:04:18.639 --> 00:04:21.509
program, so I went away from it and I

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:23.110
gained all that weight back

00:04:23.120 --> 00:04:26.150
over the course of a year just

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:27.909
eating trash again.

00:04:27.919 --> 00:04:29.270
Chick-fil-A is fine, but I was

00:04:29.280 --> 00:04:31.029
eating the fries and

00:04:31.029 --> 00:04:31.039
McDonald's

00:04:31.039 --> 00:04:32.830
fries.

00:04:32.840 --> 00:04:34.150
I don't want nobody trying to come after

00:04:34.160 --> 00:04:36.230
me like I'm talking bad about

00:04:36.230 --> 00:04:36.240
your

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:37.670
company; I'm just telling y'all I

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:39.870
like your food,

00:04:39.870 --> 00:04:39.880
but

00:04:39.880 --> 00:04:42.150
I know you have

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:44.510
healthier alternatives, Chick-fil-A.

00:04:49.280 --> 00:04:52.070
It doesn't taste as

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:56.749
good, though, Brandon. I'm just trying to say

00:04:56.759 --> 00:04:58.550
your fries are

00:04:58.560 --> 00:05:02.189
good and, golly, you get me all tickled.

00:05:02.199 --> 00:05:04.070
I'm not trying to pick at your companies;

00:05:04.080 --> 00:05:06.590
I'm just saying that's not

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:08.909
the direction I need to go anymore.

00:05:08.919 --> 00:05:12.110
We love you, Chick-fil-A;

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:13.749
you're a blessing. Put your weight goals down

00:05:13.759 --> 00:05:15.710
in the comments.

00:05:15.720 --> 00:05:18.189
Let's do it

00:05:18.199 --> 00:05:20.629
together.

00:05:20.639 --> 00:05:21.950
You don't even have to say if

00:05:21.960 --> 00:05:23.550
you're female or male

00:05:23.550 --> 00:05:23.560
because

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:25.550
girls are real sensitive

00:05:25.560 --> 00:05:28.110
to that stuff, but you can write

00:05:28.120 --> 00:05:30.350
down, 'I'm believing God for 20 pounds

00:05:30.350 --> 00:05:30.360
this year.'Every

00:05:30.360 --> 00:05:33.590
single week we'll

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:34.990
weigh in.

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:36.550
I'll try to make a video, but

00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:42.990
I'm trying to reprogram my mind to

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:44.110
think

00:05:44.120 --> 00:05:47.350
healthy. It's

00:05:47.350 --> 00:05:47.360
not

00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:50.230
an

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:52.350
excuse anymore. I'm

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:56.350
43 years old, turning 44 this year, and

00:05:56.360 --> 00:05:58.230
it's really serious. You have

00:05:58.230 --> 00:05:58.240
to

00:05:58.240 --> 00:06:00.230
start taking care of yourself, especially

00:06:00.230 --> 00:06:00.240
regarding

00:06:00.240 --> 00:06:02.710
hereditary issues your family

00:06:02.710 --> 00:06:02.720
has

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:04.189
dealt with for years. You've just

00:06:04.199 --> 00:06:06.550
got to say, 'No, that's not me. I'm not going

00:06:06.560 --> 00:06:08.990
home early.'I'm going to stick

00:06:09.000 --> 00:06:11.309
around; God has a plan for me. I have

00:06:11.319 --> 00:06:13.710
things I need to do, and so I'm not going

00:06:13.720 --> 00:06:17.390
to let weight stand in my way anymore.

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:20.510
No more strongholds.

00:06:20.520 --> 00:06:22.990
I'm finding scriptures

00:06:22.990 --> 00:06:23.000
about

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:25.909
self-control:

00:06:25.919 --> 00:06:27.550
God has not given me a spirit of

00:06:27.560 --> 00:06:29.550
fear, but of power, love, and of

00:06:29.560 --> 00:06:32.110
a sound mind. He gives you a

00:06:32.110 --> 00:06:32.120
spirit of

00:06:32.120 --> 00:06:33.950
self-control. One of the fruits of the Spirit

00:06:33.960 --> 00:06:34.950
is

00:06:34.960 --> 00:06:37.029
self-control.

00:06:37.039 --> 00:06:38.990
I don't need those things. This

00:06:38.990 --> 00:06:39.000
is

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:42.469
just something I'm talking to y'all

00:06:42.479 --> 00:06:45.950
about, just being real. I hope

00:06:45.960 --> 00:06:48.029
this blessed y'all. I know it's kind

00:06:48.039 --> 00:06:50.150
of quirky, but I'm praying

00:06:50.150 --> 00:06:50.160
and

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:52.589
believing God that I look back at this video

00:06:52.599 --> 00:06:55.869
this time next year

00:06:55.879 --> 00:06:58.110
and

00:06:58.120 --> 00:07:00.710
see

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:04.749
the

00:07:04.759 --> 00:07:06.589
turnaround.

00:07:06.599 --> 00:07:09.510
Father, I thank You for

00:07:09.520 --> 00:07:12.430
every single person here. If

00:07:12.440 --> 00:07:13.909
they need help with their weight just

00:07:13.919 --> 00:07:15.749
like me, Lord, I petition You.

00:07:15.759 --> 00:07:18.350
I thank You that this is the year of

00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:20.909
change, the year that we're not

00:07:20.919 --> 00:07:22.510
going back

00:07:22.520 --> 00:07:27.309
into that stupid pattern of eating

00:07:27.319 --> 00:07:29.950
wrong and

00:07:29.960 --> 00:07:33.110
abusing food. Father, I thank You,

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:37.469
Lord, that we use food as fuel to

00:07:37.469 --> 00:07:37.479
maintain

00:07:37.479 --> 00:07:40.589
us; it's

00:07:40.599 --> 00:07:42.830
not for comfort or enjoyment.

00:07:42.840 --> 00:07:45.830
I'm looking at it, Father, as a place of

00:07:45.840 --> 00:07:49.110
sustaining

00:07:49.120 --> 00:07:50.749
my ministry and doing what God's called

00:07:50.759 --> 00:07:52.670
me to do. It's

00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:55.189
a different mindset. Father,

00:07:55.199 --> 00:07:57.430
I thank You, Lord, that every single one

00:07:57.440 --> 00:08:01.110
of us will overcome; we overcome by the

00:08:01.120 --> 00:08:03.670
blood of the Lamb and by the word of our

00:08:03.680 --> 00:08:06.350
testimony. I thank You, Father, that

00:08:06.360 --> 00:08:08.510
there will be a great turnaround of

00:08:08.510 --> 00:08:08.520
events

00:08:08.520 --> 00:08:11.270
in each one of our lives. When

00:08:11.280 --> 00:08:14.149
we look back next year, we're

00:08:14.159 --> 00:08:16.830
going to say, 'look at what the Lord has

00:08:16.830 --> 00:08:16.840
done,'and

00:08:16.840 --> 00:08:20.110
we give You all the glory, honor,

00:08:20.120 --> 00:08:22.830
and praise for it in the name of Jesus.

00:08:24.639 --> 00:08:27.350
We ask You, God, that You help us and give us

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:29.869
supernatural weight loss.

00:08:32.320 --> 00:08:36.389
What may take some people years to do,

00:08:36.399 --> 00:08:39.230
God, may You accelerate it in our bodies

00:08:39.240 --> 00:08:42.149
to help us be

00:08:42.159 --> 00:08:44.310
healthy for You. I take

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:47.870
authority over the cravings for sugar

00:08:47.870 --> 00:08:47.880
and

00:08:47.880 --> 00:08:50.670
addictions; I thank

00:08:50.680 --> 00:08:52.870
You, Lord, that they are broken off of us

00:08:52.880 --> 00:08:55.949
in Jesus'name. We have authority over

00:08:55.959 --> 00:08:58.350
this stuff and we speak to our temple. We

00:08:58.360 --> 00:09:01.389
say, 'Body, you

00:09:01.399 --> 00:09:04.430
line up with the Word of

00:09:04.430 --> 00:09:04.440
God.'I

00:09:04.440 --> 00:09:07.829
have

00:09:07.839 --> 00:09:10.550
authority over you, flesh, and I command

00:09:10.560 --> 00:09:14.150
you to stop it right now. I command

00:09:14.150 --> 00:09:14.160
these

00:09:14.160 --> 00:09:16.949
addictions to be broken off of

00:09:16.959 --> 00:09:20.670
me right now in Jesus'name. Strongholds

00:09:20.680 --> 00:09:22.470
be

00:09:22.480 --> 00:09:25.389
gone. We believe, Father,

00:09:25.399 --> 00:09:28.389
that for whom the Son has

00:09:28.399 --> 00:09:32.230
set free is free indeed. We thank You,

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:35.670
Lord, for You are so good

00:09:35.680 --> 00:09:38.350
to us.

00:09:41.360 --> 00:09:44.030
We consider it done. You're a good God

00:09:44.040 --> 00:09:46.910
and You're faithful.

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:52.430
I hope that was encouraging to

00:09:52.430 --> 00:09:52.440
y'all

00:09:52.440 --> 00:09:55.750
today. If you like it, put a thumbs up,

00:09:55.760 --> 00:09:58.069
click that notification bell,

00:09:58.069 --> 00:09:58.079
and

00:09:58.079 --> 00:10:00.630
subscribe. It helps

00:10:00.630 --> 00:10:00.640
with

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:03.069
the algorithms, y'all. When you do

00:10:03.079 --> 00:10:05.030
that, you're getting the Gospel and

00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:07.310
videos like this out throughout the

00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:09.590
world. It helps people start clicking it,

00:10:09.600 --> 00:10:11.509
and I start getting people who are

00:10:11.509 --> 00:10:11.519
not born again

00:10:11.519 --> 00:10:12.870
looking at this;

00:10:12.880 --> 00:10:15.430
they

00:10:15.440 --> 00:10:18.470
need Jesus, and you are helping them find

00:10:18.470 --> 00:10:18.480
Him.

00:10:18.480 --> 00:10:20.790
I believe with all my heart when

00:10:20.800 --> 00:10:22.949
they watch my videos that they'll see Jesus loves

00:10:22.959 --> 00:10:24.630
them and that's going to set them free.

00:10:24.640 --> 00:10:26.829
Put a smile

00:10:26.839 --> 00:10:29.750
on your face and a song in your heart.

00:10:29.760 --> 00:10:32.509
Jesus loves you so much, and we love you.

00:10:32.519 --> 00:10:35.030
We will see you next time. Y'all have

00:10:35.040 --> 00:10:39.440
a blessed day. Bye-bye.

